description: Newly constructed in 2015, the Residences at Dahlgren Hall is a beautiful building, designed with South Boston's rich history in mind. The home features an open floor plan, perfect for entertaining. The modern kitchen offers sleek custom cabinetry, with white granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. The master bedroom comes with a large walk-in closet, with excellent storage space, and a luxurious en-suite bath; the second bedroom is spacious and sunny, with ample natural sunlight. A large roof deck offers the perfect venue to entertain guests during the summer months, with sweeping views of the city skyline. Private deeded storage and garage parking complete this home.  This stunning home is located in the heart of South Boston, placing you within close proximity to the Seaport District, and many of the city's best restaurants, shops and attractions. Easily accessible by public transportation or major highways, this home provides the perfect location for any lifestyle.
